The,Pipe,API,integrates,screen,video,recording,into,web,and,mobile,applications,It,is,available,in,JSON,data,with,XML,formats,Authentication,is,automatic,via,webhooks,although,it,provides,extra,layers,of,security,with,HTTP,and,X,Pipe,Signature,Developers,can,use,the,API,to,create,video,recording,projects,that,provide,k,to,UltraHD,quality,bandwidth,independent,MP,conversion,snapshots,and,device,rotation